# Eval result directories pile up — every run creates a new
# timestamped subdir under here. Keep them locally for debugging but
# don't commit each run.
#
# We DO commit one baseline directory (the first Tier-1 run, kept as
# `baseline_*/`) so reviewers can see the expected report shape
# without having to run the eval themselves.
*
!.gitignore
!baseline_*/
!baseline_*/**
